{"tid":171581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連葉劉都宣佈歸位啦！","createTime":"2017-03-25T11:55:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T17:40:02.000Z","uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82ef978a53e41762658a8cc5bfaa37c54510700e","tid":171581,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/74213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F74213.jpg&h=d9c052a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215402&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=6152668a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215402&h=501e3392\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=215402</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，林鄭月娥辦事能力高，最符合中央提出的四大條件，相信新民黨黨員會以此作指標。而提名曾俊華參選的金融服務界選委詹劍崙轉軚，跟隨業界投票給林鄭月娥。<br />\n<br />\n未能成功入閘參選的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀接受訪問時，拒絕表明投票意向，但批評曾俊華雖然支持度高，但政綱不實在，反而大讚林鄭月辦事能力最符合中央提出的四大條件。<br />\n<br />\n18名選委的金融服務界，其中17人發表聲明，表明投票給林鄭月娥，包括提名曾俊華的詹劍崙。<br />\n<br />\n提名階段支持胡國興的11名工程界選委，決定轉為投票支持曾俊華。<br />\n<br />\n綜合最新形勢，如果提名林鄭月娥的580名選委無走票，計上工聯會、民建聯等團體已決定一致投票給她，林鄭月娥應可取得超過600票。<br />\n<br />\n至於曾俊華暫獲的支持低於400個，包括300多個泛民選委、大部分的支持及早前提名他的30多個非泛民選委。"},{"pid":"b449dca8123828ea579860e1601ed2da0ddbd64c","tid":171581,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385623d5e26956e8dcbe4156d4adc84b181ad1a1","tid":171581,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T11:59:16.000Z","msg":"又想做保安局局長？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=